                            <comment id="13502708" author="slebresne" created="Thu, 22 Nov 2012 10:48:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think that assertion is wrong and has always been (it&apos;s definitively possible that diff is called on a tombstone). Attaching patch to fix.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For the second type of errors, this is &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-4417&quot; title=&quot;invalid counter shard detected &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-4417&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-4417&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and I&apos;m almost certain this is not related (or rather if it is, I have no clue how).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
